Because I lacked strength,
I allowed my master's life to be put
in danger...

rows.label: tlk20010151_02_msg0002
rows.name: I must become stronger to protect him.

One day, I would like to acquire an ability
useful for exploration, such as climbing
high cliffs or the like.
